title: KANU receives 12 defectors from the Jubilee Party - VIDEO | The Standard
text:
KTN Prime / 9 hours ago [VIDEO] KANU receives 12 defectors from the Jubilee Party 
The Kenyan Independence Party KANU has today received twelve defectors from the Jubilee Party. The politicians from different counties are vying for parliamentary seats and for positions in county assemblies. They were received by West Pokot Senator John Lonyangapuo and nominated Senator Zipporah Kittony. Related Videos
